[p]Hello Stellaris Community![/p][p][/p][p]We’re proud to announce that [b]#MODJAM2025[/b] is available now on the [url="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3504405585"]Stellaris Steam Workshop[/url]![/p][p][/p][h3]Subscribe on Steam: [dynamiclink href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3504405585"][/dynamiclink][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/41a37613832e3bde862c6effffa0ea1f6a3f0dea.png"][/img][/h3][p]#MODJAM2025 boasts over 15 new player crisis paths for you to explore, with more potentially coming on Thursday.[/p][p][/p][p]But that’s not all, you get to [url="http://pdxint.at/mj25vote"]vote for your five favorites[/url]! Voting closes on August 22nd, so be sure to get your votes in before then![/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/6186ed6c35113f70df55bb47febc693c72c63234.png"][/img][/p][p][/p][p]We will announce the winners of #MODJAM2025 on August 25th, with the top 3 Player Crisis Paths getting some great prizes from our sponsors at Republic of Gamers![/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/21bc1bd4f407b7fab3c37a057aa869b4832bb776.png"][/img][/p][p][/p][p]This year our first place Modder will win an ROG Ally X, and our second place Modder will win an Rog Ally, both from our sponsors at Republic of Gamers! Our third place Modder will receive a Stellaris Merchandise Bundle valued at approximately USD$170 from our friends here at Stellaris Marketing.[/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/351fe2fe78896db4b2b32c941a40f48fd0a8c7bc.png"][/img][/p][p][/p][p]Want to know more about #MODJAM2025? [url="https://www.youtube.com/@michael_stellaris"]Michael~[/url] joins us again this summer, to highlight each of the Player Crisis Paths![/p][p][/p][previewyoutube="PHPXxNpoW38;full"][/previewyoutube][p][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/stellaris-modjam2025-showcase-modded-crisis-paths-part-1.1846937/"]Submission #1 Highlight on the Stellaris Forums[/url][/p][p][/p][previewyoutube="hZY40bdRLGc;full"][/previewyoutube][p][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/stellaris-modjam2025-showcase-modded-crisis-paths-part-2.1851735/"]Submission #2 Highlight on the Stellaris Forums[/url][/p][p][/p][previewyoutube="YnxQYoZC-6I;full"][/previewyoutube][p][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/stellaris-modjam2025-showcase-modded-crisis-paths-part-3.1852883/"]Submission #3 Highlight on the Stellaris Forums[/url][/p][p][/p][p]Thanks to everyone who signed up, contributed, helped test, and of course thank you for our sponsors for supporting #MODJAM2025![/p][p][/p][p][b]Subscribe today![/b][/p][p]Steam: [/p][p][url="https://pdxint.at/mj25steam"]https://pdxint.at/mj25steam[/url][/p][p]Paradox Mods: [/p][p][url="https://pdxint.at/mj25pdxmods"]https://pdxint.at/mj25pdxmods[/url][/p][p]Vote: [/p][p][url="http://pdxint.at/mj25vote"]http://pdxint.at/mj25vote[/url][/p][p][/p][p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/4f5b5f07c6e8e505fadfa06b8a86751a45b45532.png"][/img][/p]